  "excerpt": "<p>Get started managing and analyzing your metadata with DataTools Pro</p>",
  "content_html": "\n<div class=\"wp-block-genesis-blocks-gb-columns gb-layout-columns-1 one-column\"><div class=\"gb-layout-column-wrap gb-block-layout-column-gap-2 gb-is-responsive-column\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-genesis-blocks-gb-column gb-block-layout-column\"><div class=\"gb-block-layout-column-inner\">\n<p class=\"wp-embed-aspect-4-3 wp-has-aspect-ratio\">Thank you for signing up for DataTools Pro! We want to make getting started with our tools as easy a possible! Here are resources to get you moving forward.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading wp-embed-aspect-4-3 wp-has-aspect-ratio has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-f83198436f9007b32ace96dd2f97f252\" style=\"color:#656c73\">Step 1 Connect your Salesforce Objects</h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-embed-aspect-4-3 wp-has-aspect-ratio\">The first step to using DataTools Pro dictionary and entity relationship diagrams is to add Salesforce objects. Click on the &#8220;Guided Tour&#8221; button to walk you step by step.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading wp-embed-aspect-4-3 wp-has-aspect-ratio has-text-color has-link-color has-medium-font-size wp-elements-1ddbbd9cead0e55e0b057c346fb28302\" style=\"color:#656c73\">More resources to learn DataTools Pro</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>To access support resources for this page or any tool, simply click on the help icon for contextual articles and videos. You can also re-launch this getting started window and re-watch the guided tour anytime!</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img data-dominant-color=\"cdd3d3\" data-has-transparency=\"true\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"892\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/image-16.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-9561 has-transparency\" style=\"--dominant-color: #cdd3d3; width:257px;height:auto\" srcset=\"https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/image-16.png 892w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/image-16-300x180.png 300w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/image-16-768x460.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 892px) 100vw, 892px\" /></figure>\n</div></div>\n</div></div>\n"
